Mounting Procedure
==================

|Product| can be mounted with 4 x **M4** (6mm) screws using the **VESA** (100x100mm or 75x75mm).

|Product| can be mounted with **panel mounting** method, enabling simplified installation onto any standard mounting fixture.

.. attention::

    Please make sure the display is not exposed to high pressure when mounting into an enclosure.

You can find detailed information about mounting in the |mguide|.